# 🏗️ Networking Chatbot — Complete System Architecture

> **Stack:** Node.js + Express.js | MongoDB Atlas (Vector Search) | Google Sheets API | 11za WhatsApp Platform  
> **Project:** `d:\VectorSearch - Copy` (existing codebase ke upar build hoga)

---

## 📐 1. Complete System Architecture Overview

```mermaid
flowchart TD
    A[WhatsApp User] -->|Message| B(11za WhatsApp Platform)
    B -->|Webhook POST| C[Express.js Backend\napp.js / routes/flow.js]
    C --> D{Controller\nflowController.js}

    D --> E[Recommendation Engine]
    D --> F[Connection Request Service]
    D --> G[Notification Service]

    E --> H[(MongoDB Atlas\nVector Search)]
    F --> H
    G --> I[11za Template Message API]

    E --> J[Google Sheets Logger]
    F --> J

    H --> K[users collection]
    H --> L[seen_recommendations collection]
    H --> M[connection_requests collection]
    H --> N[daily_limits collection]
```

