## 🤖 7. Complete Chatbot Flow Logic (11za WhatsApp)

```
USER → "Main networking recommendations dekhna chahta hoon"
         │
         ▼
    [NODE: GET_USER_PROFILE]
    API: POST /checkUserProfile { phone }
    ├── Profile exists? Continue
    └── No profile? → "Pehle register karein"
         │
         ▼
    [NODE: GET_CATEGORY]
    API: POST /getCategoryByUser { phone }
    Returns: user.category[] e.g. ["Startup", "Investor"]
         │
         ▼
    [NODE: CHECK_DAILY_LIMIT]
    API: POST /checkDailyLimit { phone }
    ├── count >= 5? → "Aaj ke 5 recommendations ho gaye. Kal dobara aayein! 🙏"
    └── count < 5? → Continue
         │
         ▼
    [NODE: GET_NEXT_RECOMMENDATION]
    API: POST /getNextRecommendation { phone, category, excludeIds: [] }
         │
    ┌────┴─────────────────────────────────────────────┐
    │                                                  │
    ▼                                                  ▼
[RESULT: Profile Found]                    [RESULT: No More Available]
    │                                                  │
    ▼                                          "🙏 Thank You!"
Show Profile Card:                         "No More Recommendations"
- Name                                     "Aap saare profiles dekh chuke hain"
- Company                                  "Naye log join hone par aapko inform karenge"
- Category
- Bio (short)
- Link1 / Link2
         │
         ▼
    User Choice:
    [1] → "Connect Request Bhejna Chahta Hoon"
    [2] → "Agle Profile Dekhna Hai"
    [3] → "Main Yahan Se Ruk Jaata Hoon"
         │
    ┌────┼────┐
    ▼    ▼    ▼
   [1]  [2]  [3]
         │
   [1] SEND REQUEST
   API: POST /sendConnectionRequest { senderPhone, receiverPhone }
   ├── MongoDB: Insert connection_request (status: pending)
   ├── Google Sheet: Log event
   └── 11za: Send template to receiverPhone → "XYZ ne aapko connect karna chahte hain" 
              → receiverPhone: [Accept] / [Reject] buttons
         │
         ▼
   [2] NEXT RECOMMENDATION
   API: POST /getNextRecommendation (loop — excludeIds mein seen add karke)
         │
         ▼
   [3] END SESSION
   "Theek hai! Jab bhi networking karna ho, hum yahan hain 🤝"

────────────────────────────────────────
RECEIVER SIDE FLOW (User B):
────────────────────────────────────────
User B accepts → Button webhook → 
API: POST /acceptConnectionRequest { senderPhone, receiverPhone }
├── MongoDB: status = "accepted", acceptedAt = now
├── Google Sheet: Log
└── 11za: Send template to senderPhone → "🎉 [UserB] ne aapki request accept kar li!"

User B rejects → 
API: POST /rejectConnectionRequest { senderPhone, receiverPhone }
├── MongoDB: status = "rejected"
└── Google Sheet: Log (no notification to sender — silent reject)
```

