## 🚀 13. Scaling Considerations

| Area | Current | Scalable Approach |
|------|---------|-------------------|
| **Seen IDs** | User document mein array | ✅ Separate `seen_recommendations` collection |
| **Daily Limit** | Not implemented | ✅ `daily_limits` collection + TTL index |
| **Duplicate Requests** | Basic check | ✅ Compound unique index on `{senderPhone, receiverPhone}` |
| **Vector Search** | Single $vectorSearch | ✅ Keep as-is, Atlas handles scaling |
| **Google Sheet** | Not implemented | ✅ Async, non-blocking logger utility |
| **Exclusion Query** | Max ~50 IDs | ✅ For 1000+ IDs → migrate to `$lookup` join |

---

## ⚠️ 14. Current Codebase Gaps (Jo Fix Karna Hai)

> [!WARNING]
> Ye issues tumhare existing [flowController.js](file:///d:/VectorSearch%20-%20Copy/controller/flowController.js) mein hain jo fix karne hain.

1. **`alreadyShown` flag** — [searchUserByCategoryAndBio()](file:///d:/VectorSearch%20-%20Copy/controller/flowController.js#296-358) mein global `alreadyShown` use ho raha hai. Yeh per-user nahi hai. Replace karo `seen_recommendations` collection se.

2. **Daily Limit** — Abhi koi daily limit nahi hai. `daily_limits` collection banana hai.

3. **No End State** — Jab saari recommendations dekh li jaayein, system loop mein jaata hai. `isEnd: true` flag aur proper "Thank You" message add karna hai.

4. **[sendConnectionRequest](file:///d:/VectorSearch%20-%20Copy/controller/flowController.js#995-1127)** — Function abhi properly implement nahi hai controller mein. Banana hai.

5. **Google Sheet Logger** — Abhi koi logging nahi hai. `utilities/googleSheetLogger.js` banana hai.

6. **`$vectorSearch` mein filter** — Abhi `$match` vectorSearch ke baad hai. Better hoga `preFilter` use karo (Atlas Vector Search supports it).

---

